{"tid":484862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(本土派) 林忌: 非禮受害人不報警, 是可以理解","createTime":"2017-11-30T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T14:12:16.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"80a6be02d2dd7dff649e02f47d8d869e93f5a653","tid":484862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10154889474971121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10154889474971121&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0jizA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9bcdd9b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10154889474971121</a><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam<br />\n42分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一個非禮受害人選擇報警，或者唔報，總有佢自己的理由；舉例說，有更多不想啟齒，影響未來生活的案情（純舉例），如果上庭被揭晒出來，寧願唔告係完全可以理解<br />\n<br />\n唔好再傷害佢啦</span><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam <span style=\"color: blue;\">其實倒返轉，the accused 亦有言論自由去反駁，甚至告佢誹謗<br />\n讚好</span><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam <span style=\"color: blue;\">如果女方無中生有，男方可以立即控告女方誹謗，到時舉證責任全在女方</span><br />\n<br />\nTakki Ma <span style=\"color: green;\">但係女方唔name的話告唔告得？</span><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam <span style=\"color: blue;\">如果唔 name, 又估唔到，當然難告；但唔 name，卻被人估到，已經可以告誹謗</span>"},{"pid":"d594a25a77d765c21051bf0ae4dae3d5c9b85b0a","tid":484862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a556ab1b90229468cee38801ade98d0caa9ea5","tid":484862,"uid":4783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"林忌就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d336ad378e03daf694473a77554c0f657b3a7e4","tid":484862,"uid":54876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"閘住反彈<br />\n無人覺得林忌係本土派喎"},{"pid":"b1a602f51eb99e7dc899fa910f6cbad8cdad120a","tid":484862,"uid":123774,"li